## *Informative VAT calculation* ##
-----

As part of localization pack, option to calculate informative VAT is added. It is used in cases when VAT value is 0, but informative value needs to be calculated and later added to invoice printout or other documents.

### Setup ###
_Tax/Undirect Taxes/Sales Tax/Sales Tax Codes/Values_

Informative value % field is added to Sales Tax Codes Values. 

